casebody.data:
Manuel V. ANTUNA, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
STATE of Florida, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D17-3032 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. February 1, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

This appeal is dismissed as from a nonfinal, nonappealable order. See Fla. R. App. P. 9.030(b)(1)(A), .140(b)(1)(D) ; Stevens v. State, 57 So.3d 960 (Fla. 2D DCA 2011).

Appellant's January 16, 2018, "Motion to Dismiss Petition" is denied as moot.

NORTHCUTT, CRENSHAW, and MORRIS, JJ., Concur.
